---
import { changeLanguage, t } from "i18next";
import "../styles/global.css";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

changeLanguage("en");

const pageTitle = t("about.title");
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <h2>Vladyslav Sapkovych</h2>

  <p>Award-winning software engineer from Ukraine, pursuing Computer Science degree at Technical University of Košice, Faculty of Electrical Engineering and Informatics. Specialize in Python, JS, C#, Lua for AI, web, and game modding. Expert in reverse engineering. Open-source contributor, regional CS Olympiad winner. Reach me at sapkovich.vladislav@gmail.com or <a href="https://github.com/Nominy">GitHub</a></p>

  <h3>Skills</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Languages/Frameworks: Python, PyTorch, C#, Lua, JS/TypeScript (React, Next.js, Svelte, Express.js), GDScript, C++</li>
    <li>Tools/Platforms: Unity, Unreal Engine 4 (UE4SS), Blender API, SQLite, GitHub Actions, Linux</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Key Projects</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>RimMercenaries (RimWorld Mod, 2025): 14k+ views, 3.5k+ subscribers. Complex C# systems, XML enhancements.</li>
    <li>Hidden-Bat Detector (PyTorch, 2023): ResNet50 fine-tuned on synthetic data; 35% pass@1 accuracy.</li>
    <li>Payday 3 Audio Mod (UE4SS, 2025): Reverse-engineered audio via Wwise API.</li>
    <li>vk-kiriban-catcher (Next.js, 2024): Real-time VK milestone tracker with WebSockets.</li>
    <li>io scene mdl (Blender Addon, 2023): Reverse-engineered .mdl format importer/exporter.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Open Source & Community</h3>
  <p>Contributor to GitHub developer tools and algorithm libraries. Volunteer DevOps & Lua Developer, Crystal Horizons GMod Server (2024–2025). Tutored 30+ students in programming, math, physics.</p>

  <h3>Education & Honors</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Gold Medal Graduate, Economic Lyceum of Odesa (2025, GPA 4.9/5)</li>
    <li>Winner, Odesa Region CS Olympiad (Python), 2023 & 2024</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Languages</h3>
  <p>English, Ukrainian, Russian (Fluent); German, Slovak (Intermediate); Chinese, Spanish (Basic)</p>

  <h3>Interests</h3>
  <p>Reverse Engineering, AI Interpretability, Procedural Generation, Algorithm Visualization</p>
</BaseLayout>
